definition.value: A member of the class of pterocarpans that is 3-hydroxyptercarpan with a methoxy substituent at position 9.
An aminobenzoic acid that is anthranilic acid substituted by a hydroxy group at position 3 and a methyl group at position 4.
An N-acetyl-D-galactosaminyl group in which D-Gal is linked beta(1->3) to the D-GalNAc group which has alpha-configuration at its anomeric centre.
